" class="sites-navigation-link">三皈［五戒、八戒］十戒文</a></div></li><li class=""><div dir="ltr" style="padding-left: 38px;"><a href="/site/palishengdian/refer/savaka" jotId="wuid:gx:39fcd81728406621" class="sites-navigation-link">佛子行</a></div></li><li class=""><div dir="ltr" style="padding-left: 38px;"><a href="/site/palishengdian/refer/savaka2" jotId="wuid:gx:2bc26164ca09932e" class="sites-navigation-link">佛子行之二</a></div></li><li class=""><div dir="ltr" style="padding-left: 38px;"><a href="/site/palishengdian/refer/flag" jotId="wuid:gx:49b28305a85c5eb" class="sites-navigation-link">佛教旗</a></div></li><li class=""><div dir="ltr" style="padding-left: 38px;"><a href="/site/palishengdian/refer/era" jotId="wuid:gx:79dfef92bee43707" class="sites-navigation-link">佛曆 B.E.</a></div></li><li class=""><div dir="ltr" style="padding-left: 38px;"><a href="/site/palishengdian/refer/mula" jotId="wuid:gx:4eaa6ea41983df7b" class="sites-navigation-link">佛法綱要</a></div></li><li class=""><div dir="ltr" style="padding-left: 38px;"><a href="/site/palishengdian/refer/nibbana" jotId="wuid:gx:1aeda62f5b1723b" class="sites-navigation-link">佛遺教經</a></div></li><li class=""><div dir="ltr" style="padding-left: 38px;"><a href="/site/palishengdian/refer/india" jotId="wuid:gx:257341c9f91e4bdc" class="sites-navigation-link">印度月份</a></div></li><li class=""><div dir="ltr" style="padding-left: 38px;"><a href="/site/palishengdian/refer/rupa" jotId="wuid:gx:73d14b530295bba0" class="sites-navigation-link">圖解佛法</a></div></li><li class=""><div dir="ltr" style="padding-left: 38px;"><a href="/site/palishengdian/refer/olcott" jotId="wuid:gx:2ba294c31175658" class="sites-navigation-link">奧爾科特 Olcott</a></div></li><li class=""><div dir="ltr" style="padding-left: 38px;"><a href="/site/palishengdian/refer/history" jotId="wuid:gx:19a69062bfcd74f5" class="sites-navigation-link">巴利文大藏經</a></div></li><li class=""><div dir="ltr" style="padding-left: 38px;"><a href="/site/palishengdian/refer/pts" jotId="wuid:gx:1f57678098bd4445" c